♪ And the call of spring

00:00:32.249 --> 00:00:34.752 position:21% line:89% align:start
♪ Gives me strength

00:00:34.785 --> 00:00:38.421 position:19% line:89% align:start
♪ And courage to know

00:00:38.455 --> 00:00:42.524 position:13% line:5% align:start
♪ I will make it through

00:00:42.558 --> 00:00:46.528 position:7% line:5% align:start
♪ Whatever life throws at me

